<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:06:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列高级警官被指控性行为不端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</link><description>这名被指控违反信任罪的警官还被勒令离开车站一周。这名妇女正在嫌疑人监管的警察局中作为志愿者完成国民服役</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列进入世界显微镜，海牙为期两天的种族灭绝听证会结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</link><description>南非和以色列在国际法院种族灭绝案中提出初步论点后，以色列在加沙的行为和政治言论成为世界关注的焦点。接下来的事情由法庭决定</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</guid></item><item><title>“我有土地，但我没有”：西岸橄榄收成是加沙战争的又一受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</link><description>加沙战争使约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的生活变得困难。除了检查站和封闭的道路外，橄榄园也被宣布为禁区。上周收割结束后，三分之一的农作物仍留在树上，剥夺了巴勒斯坦人生计的一个关键要素</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</guid></item><item><title>美国继续打击也门胡塞武装；火箭弹袭击加沙边境社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</link><description>以色列国防军称，约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，三名恐怖分子被打死 ■ 美国袭击萨那的胡塞武装目标 ■ 根据卡塔尔斡旋的协议，药品将在“未来几天内”转移给加沙的以色列人质。查看更多药品进入加沙</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 03:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，以色列国防军击毙三名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</link><description>周五晚上，三名枪手渗透到约旦河西岸的阿多拉定居点，通过外围围栏的缺口进入，并在与以色列国防军的交火中丧生。建议居民将自己锁在家里直到早上</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 22:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>南非犹太板球运动员在世界杯前被解除 U-19 国家队队长职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</link><description>大卫·蒂格因公开支持在加沙作战的以色列士兵而被正式免职，原因是即将举行的 19 岁以下板球世界杯存在安全问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:41:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，药品将在“未来几天内”转移给加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</link><description>卡塔尔斡旋的协议将允许向以色列人质提供处方药，而以色列将允许更多药品进入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 18:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长和国家检察官办公室因未调查 NSO 向加纳出售 Pegasus 间谍软件而受到谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-reprimanded-for-not-investigating-sale-of-pegasus-spyware-to-ghana/0000018c-fdff-d832-a59d-fdff63900000</link><description>超过 50 人组成的团体提请注意对外交部和国防部官员批准该交易的方式的怀疑</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-reprimanded-for-not-investigating-sale-of-pegasus-spyware-to-ghana/0000018c-fdff-d832-a59d-fdff63900000</guid></item><item><title>“严重扭曲”：以色列在世界法院听证会上拒绝加沙种族灭绝指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</link><description>以色列呼吁国际法院以毫无根据为由驳回该案，并驳回南非关于停止以色列国防军在加沙行动的请愿。以色列代表：整个案件“取决于对现实的故意策划、脱节和操纵性描述”</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院听证会上，以色列尽管政客愚笨，但仍提出强有力的辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</link><description>海牙的种族灭绝事件并不是由不成比例的军事反应或大量巴勒斯坦人伤亡引发的。这是以色列政治特征的直接结果：鲁莽和煽动性的冗长，而以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对此予以纵容。他甚至添加了一些自己的宝石</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的“战线统一”也增强了伊朗国内代理人的地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</link><description>真主党、也门胡塞武装和伊拉克什叶派民兵组织已经在国内的战斗中取得了成果，而且他们并不打算在加沙战争结束后停止。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</guid></item><item><title>一系列失败证明以色列安全理念已经过时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</link><description>情报一次又一次失败，现在两线作战，平民后方遭受前所未有的攻势。以色列国防军的威慑力曾有效应对 20 世纪 60 年代的威胁，但如今需要不同的解决方案。旧制度已经破产</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 13:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</guid></item><item><title>五十万加沙人正在遭受严重饥饿。让其沉入其中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</link><descript