rful-message-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-fb01-d517-af9d-ff3fc49a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：伊朗是胡塞武装和其他组织袭击以色列的主要推动者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</link><description>在此之前，美国领导的联军袭击也门胡塞武装目标，以回应数月来对红海海上交通的袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 02:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/u-s-iran-is-primary-enabler-of-houthis-and-other-groups-attacking-israel/0000018c-fb6d-d517-af9d-ff7fb9bb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>